column294: Welcome to this spectacular newly made luxury duplex penthouse. Excellent located in a house from 1880s with decorative details at Térez körut with windows looking at Király utca. The duplex penthouse has the size of 133 m2 and a terrace of 32 m2 (This means a total of 149 m2 in the apartments papers since you add half the size of the terrace). The apartment has a kitchen open with the living room, two bedroom, three bathrooms and an outdoor jacuzzi on the terrace. Minimalistic kitchen equipped with white LG HI-MACS work top. Living room with 5, 6 meter plus ceilings and huge windows. The master bedroom suite has hotel feeling and is open with the bathroom. The apartment has wooden floors, air-conditions, alarm system and built in multiroom audio system (8 pair of speakers built in the celling). The terrace is perfect for relaxing in the jaccuzzi or entertaining. Nerby a garageplace is inluded in the apartment. Very close to Octogon, Liszt Ferenc tér, Andrássy út and public communication. In the neighborhood you find a lot of popular restaurants. Internet, cable-TV, phone line, cleaning and washing service can be arranged for an extra fee. The apartment can be rented with or without furniture.
